Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:12.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,6000)\fs24\pos(85.044,531)}文化史\N『集群的百年構想』\N多媒體教學\N\N高一・高二\N請遵守截止時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:39.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\fs40}進化與多樣性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:45.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an9}班級目標 時刻意識到自己是集群的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}人類定義的變化\N　智人　　能人　→　集人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx60\fscy60\pos(67.035,89)}Homo Sapiens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx60\fscy60\pos(175.091,89)}Homo Habilis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx60\fscy60\pos(317.166,89)}Homo Establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:53.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fnHYXuanSong 85S\c&HAEDE92&\fs40\pos(960,114)\alpha&H80&}逃離集群是窮兇極惡的犯罪行為\N是站在人類對立面的敵對行動
